---
---
<section id="about" class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Text & Methodology Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-6">
        <div>
          <!-- Subsection Header with Industrial Accent Bar -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-8 bg-accent block"></span>
            <h2 class="text-xs font-condensed font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">COMPANY OVERVIEW</h2>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-condensed font-bold text-brand-navy uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">
            A Culture of Technical Discipline
          </h3>
          
          <p class="text-slate-650 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 font-sans">
            3D Structures was established with a singular objective — to deliver uncompromising quality in structural steel detailing. Supporting steel fabricators, EPC contractors, and structural engineering firms globally, we operate as an extended engineering partner to deliver technically robust, fabrication-ready solutions.
          </p>

          <p class="text-slate-650 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8 font-sans">
            Our structural detailing team supports projects across Australia through structured engineering workflows and disciplined execution processes. We combine the oversight of experienced senior checkers with highly skilled modeling engineers to guarantee technical compliance and project delivery schedule reliability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- The Structured Approach Grid -->
        <div class="border-t border-slate-200 pt-6">
          <h4 class="font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm text-brand-navy mb-4">OUR GUIDING PRINCIPLES</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-2.5">
              <span class="bg-slate-100 text-brand-blue p-1 rounded-none mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-700">Standard Compliance</h5>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Strict adherence to Australian standards (AS 4100, AS 1100) and fabricator-specific guidelines.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-2.5">
              <span class="bg-slate-100 text-brand-blue p-1 rounded-none mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-700">Realistic Scheduling</h5>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Milestone planning and schedule transparency that respects erection deadlines.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-2.5">
              <span class="bg-slate-100 text-brand-blue p-1 rounded-none mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"></path></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-700">Defined Responsibility</h5>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Assigned roles for estimators, senior checkers, and modelers to eliminate rework.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-2.5">
              <span class="bg-slate-100 text-brand-blue p-1 rounded-none mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z"></path></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-700">Structured Quality Control</h5>
                <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-0.5">Internal multi-stage check systems before final files are exported or issued.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Highlights / Technical Sidebar Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white p-8 border-l-4 border-accent flex flex-col justify-between h-full relative">
          <!-- Background grid decoration -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 blueprint-grid-dark opacity-10 z-0"></div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-condensed font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wide border-b border-slate-800 pb-3 text-accent">
              Operational Statistics
            </h4>
            
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Our structured workflow and scale ensure that we can resource large structural shop drawing packages under short deadlines. With a robust team of engineers, we deliver precision detailing from concept through to fabrication-ready documentation — on time, every time.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-5 pt-2">
              <!-- Item 1 -->
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-slate-350 tracking-wider">TEKLA SOFTWARE CAPACITY</span>
                <span class="font-condensed font-extrabold text-white text-base">Robust Modelling Seats</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Item 2 -->
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-slate-350 tracking-wider">TOTAL MANPOWER</span>
                <span class="font-condensed font-extrabold text-white text-base">40+ Structural Engineers</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Item 3 -->
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-slate-350 tracking-wider">QA STANDARDS CHECKLISTS</span>
                <span class="font-condensed font-extrabold text-white text-base">Multi-Level Check</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Item 4 -->
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-slate-350 tracking-wider">INFRASTRUCTURE UPTIME</span>
                <span class="font-condensed font-extrabold text-white text-base">24-Hour Operation</span>
              </div>
              <!-- Item 5 -->
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-bold uppercase text-slate-350 tracking-wider">COLLABORATION SECURITY</span>
                <span class="font-condensed font-extrabold text-white text-base">Secure Cloud Sharing</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>


        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
